Jo Peninsulas 8:15 PM
Hi Sarah, thank you for your interest! The meeting would be with me, Jo Peninsulas, and potentially one of our Earth Day 2023 project coordinators, depending on the specific topics you'd like to discuss. We're here to provide information about our initiatives and explore potential collaboration opportunities with you and BranchPattern.

To schedule a meeting, please use the following link to find a suitable time slot that works best for you: <https://bit.ly/Meet-With-ForTreesClub>

Looking forward to connecting and discussing Earth Day 2023 with you!

Best regards,
Jo
